---
title: Vegan Beans ’n’ Greens Stuffed Peppers with Creamy Hummus
description: Mild, earthy, sweet, and perfect for stuffing, bell peppers are one of our favorite ingredients for a quick (and delicious!) weeknight dinner idea. For this vegan spin on a classic, we toss springy, scallion-flecked pearl couscous with Italian-seasoned cannellini beans, kale, and tomatoes to make a hearty, flavorful stuffing. Once filled and baked, the peppers are topped with a drizzle of garlicky hummus sauce before serving. After dinner, you’ll be pleasantly stuffed, too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-beans-n-greens-stuffed-peppers-74a5c569.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/vegan-beans-n-greens-stuffed-peppers-6447d7b284d017c9de0d9f33-307db94c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/vegan-beans-n-greens-stuffed-peppers-6447d7b284d017c9de0d9f33
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 680 kcal
